<div class="product-grid-item js-product-wrapper js-grid-product " data-title="The Glossybounce™ Collection" data-price="130.00" data-variant="43919947006128" data-product-handle="the-glossybounce-collection">

  
  <script type="application/json" class="js-product-data" data-id="7722246766768" data-handle="the-glossybounce-collection">
    {"id":7722246766768,"title":"The Glossybounce™ Collection","handle":"the-glossybounce-collection","description":"\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFor the gloss-lover in your life. This limited edition wreath includes the full collection of our bestselling, high-shine Glossybounce™ lip gloss-oils for juicy, kissable lips. All nine, sheer and shimmer, shades pre-wrapped and ready to gift in sustainable paper packaging. Extremely limited quantities. Grab and gift yours before it sells out! \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAll holiday sets are pre-wrapped in sustainable, 100% FSC-certified limited edition holiday paper packaging– perfect for grabbing and gifting! Simply recycle at home once unwrapped.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSHADE DESCRIPTIONS:\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFull-Size Glossybounce™ in Kiss – Clear\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFull-Size Glossybounce™ in Dip – Dusty Rose\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFull-Size Glossybounce™ in Play – Bright Pink\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFull-Size Glossybounce™ in Bounce – Mauve \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFull-Size Glossybounce™ in Push – Soft Brown\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFull-Size Glossybounce™ in Dream – Berry\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFull-Size Glossybounce™ in \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDisco - \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePinky rose shimmer\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFull-Size Glossybounce™ in \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eShake - \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eWarm nude shimmer\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003c\/span\u003eFull-Size Glossybounce™ in Remix - Mauve shimmer\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e","published_at":"2024-10-19T00:00:02-04:00","created_at":"2024-09-23T16:12:25-04:00","vendor":"Saie","type":"Finished Good","tags":["gifts","holiday","kits","lip","lips","new"],"price":13000,"price_min":13000,"price_max":13000,"available":true,"price_varies":false,"compare_at_price":19800,"compare_at_price_min":19800,"compare_at_price_max":19800,"compare_at_price_varies":false,"variants":[{"id":43919947006128,"title":"Default Title","option1":"Default Title","option2":null,"option3":null,"sku":"GBHOLWREATH","requires_shipping":true,"taxable":true,"featured_image":null,"available":true,"name":"The Glossybounce™ Collection","public_title":null,"options":["Default Title"],"price":13000,"weight":0,"compare_at_price":19800,"inventory_management":"shopify","barcode":"810029482943","requires_selling_plan":false,"selling_plan_allocations":[],"quantity_rule":{"min":1,"max":null,"increment":1}}],"images":["\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20241126044550\/https:\/\/saiehello.com\/cdn\/shop\/files\/saieglossybouncecollection.jpg