549","width":1080},{"alt":"common","id":27242260889776,"position":5,"preview_image":{"aspect_ratio":1.0,"height":1080,"width":1080,"src":"\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20241126044550\/https:\/\/saiehello.com\/cdn\/shop\/files\/0002_2802999-av-03.jpg?v=1727118549"},"aspect_ratio":1.0,"height":1080,"media_type":"image","src":"\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20241126044550\/https:\/\/saiehello.com\/cdn\/shop\/files\/0002_2802999-av-03.jpg?v=1727118549","width":1080}],"requires_selling_plan":false,"selling_plan_groups":[],"content":"\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAn effortless, healthy flush has never been easier… or cuter! This trio of ultra-blendable cream-gel blushes contains mini sizes of best-selling Dew Blush shades Baby (baby pink), Chilly (mauve), and NEW! limited edition shade Flirty (bright watermelon).\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAll holiday sets are pre-wrapped in sustainable, 100% FSC-certified limited edition holiday paper packaging– perfect for grabbing and gifting! Simply recycle at home once unwrapped.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSHADE DESCRIPTIONS:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\n\u003cp role=\"presentation\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMini Dew Blush in Baby - baby pink\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\n\u003cp role=\"presentation\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMini Dew Blush in Chilly - mauve\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\n\u003cp role=\"presentation\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNEW + Limited Edition! Mini Dew Blush in Flirty - bright watermelon\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e \u003