"height":2500,"media_type":"image","src":"\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20241126044550\/https:\/\/saiehello.com\/cdn\/shop\/products\/slip-tint-celebration-shade-10_2.jpg?v=1708982094","width":2500},{"alt":"common","id":22340131815600,"position":97,"preview_image":{"aspect_ratio":1.0,"height":2000,"width":2000,"src":"\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20241126044550\/https:\/\/saiehello.com\/cdn\/shop\/products\/SlipTintArmSwatches_1.jpg?v=1708982094"},"aspect_ratio":1.0,"height":2000,"media_type":"image","src":"\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20241126044550\/https:\/\/saiehello.com\/cdn\/shop\/products\/SlipTintArmSwatches_1.jpg?v=1708982094","width":2000},{"alt":null,"id":26069122744496,"position":98,"preview_image":{"aspect_ratio":1.0,"height":2500,"width":2500,"src":"\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20241126044550\/https:\/\/saiehello.com\/cdn\/shop\/files\/slip-tint-celebration-shade-7_2.jpg?v=1708982049"},"aspect_ratio":1.0,"height":2500,"media_type":"image","src":"\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20241126044550\/https:\/\/saiehello.com\/cdn\/shop\/files\/slip-tint-celebration-shade-7_2.jpg?v=1708982049","width":2500},{"alt":null,"id":26827947311280,"position":99,"preview_image":{"aspect_ratio":1.0,"height":1500,"width":1500,"src":"\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20241126044550\/https:\/\/saiehello.com\/cdn\/shop\/files\/Saie_Slip_Tint_Relaunch_shade_03.55_0a125d3b-7806-4b7e-8e8b-c7b8a65acd14.png?v=1721847189"},"aspect_ratio":1.0,"height":1500,"media_type":"image","src":"\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20241126044550\/https:\/\/saiehello.com\/cdn\/shop\/files\/Saie_Slip_Tint_Relaunch_shade_03.55_0a125d3b-7806-4b7e-8e8b-c7b8a65acd14.png?v=1721847189","width":1500}],"requires_selling_plan":false,"selling_plan_groups":[{"id":"a512f6c324b2a37f8701ef638bed9aba2c7a8cd1","name":"Subscribe \u0026 Save 10%","options":[{"name":"Selling plan name","position":1,"values":["Every 1 month","Every 2 months","Every 3 months","Every 4 months"]}],"selling_plans":[{"id":2080047280,"name":"Every 1 month","description":null,"options":[{"name":"Selling plan name","position":1,"value":"Every 1 month"}],"recurring_deliveries":true,"price_adjustments":[{"order_count":null,"position":1,"value_type":"percentage","value":10}],"checkout_charge":{"value_type":"percentage","value":100}},{"id":2080080048,"name":"Every 2 months","description":null,"options":[{"name":"Selling plan name","position":1,"value":"Every 2 months"}],"recurring_deliveries":true,"price_adjustments":[{"order_count":null,"position":1,"value_type":"percentage","value":10}],"checkout_charge":{"value_type":"percentage","value":100}},{"id":2080112816,"name":"Every 3 months","description":null,"options":[{"name":"Selling plan name","position":1,"value":"Every 3 months"}],"recurring_deliveries":true,"price_adjustments":[{"order_count":null,"position":1,"value_type":"percentage","value":10}],"checkout_charge":{"value_type":"percentage","value":100}},{"id":2082439344,"name":"Every 4 months","description":null,"options":[{"name":"Selling plan name","position":1,"value":"Every 4 months"}],"recurring_deliveries":true,"price_adjustments":[{"order_count":null,"position":1,"value_type":"percentage","value":10}],"checkout_charge":{"value_type":"percentage","value":100}}],"app_id":"Yotpo Echo"}],"content":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003eSlip into something effortless, award-winning, and multitasking. Slip Tint Tinted Moisturizer sheer shades provide just enough coverage to even your complexion and give you an easy, no-makeup makeup look. Powered by Saie Science, Slip Tint Tinted Moisturizer’s formula is supercharged with clean ingredients like \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003eHyaluronic Acid to hydrate, Licorice Root Extract to visibly brighten, and 100% Mineral Non-Nano Zinc Oxide SPF 35 to protect against UVA\/UVB rays and free radical damage. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003eEach shade has been crafted to seamlessly blend into a wide range of skin tones and creates that hydrated, Signature SaieGlow™\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cstrong style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'San Francisco', 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003eSlip Tint is also dimethicone free, paraben free, talc free, silicone free, synthetic dye free, phthalate free, essential oil free, soy free, natural \u0026amp; synthetic fragrance-free, formulated without gluten \u0026amp; cruelty free. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"sh-color-black sh-color\"\u003e\u003cstrong style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'San Francisco', 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003eGet to know these effective, luxury ingredients:\u003cspan class=\"gmail-Apple-converted-space sh-color-black sh-color\"\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"sh-color-black sh-color\"\u003e⁃Hyaluronic Acid deeply hydrates\u003cspan class=\"gmail-Apple-converted-space sh-color-black sh-color\"\u003e \u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e⁃Licorice Root extract brightens and refines\u003cspan class=\"gmail-Apple-converted-space sh-color-black sh-color\"\u003e \u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e⁃100% mineral zinc-oxide offers clean SPF protection\u003cbr\u003e⁃Pansy Flower fights free radicals and delivers antioxidants\u003cspan class=\"gmail-Apple-converted-space sh-color-black sh-color\"\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"sh-color-black sh-color\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"gmail-Apple-converted-space sh-color-black sh-color\"\u003e\u003cmeta charset=\"utf-8\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eCheck out our \u003ca href=\"https:\/\/saiehello.com\/pages\/find-your-shade\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eshade finder\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/a\u003e to find your match!\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"p1\"\u003eBest Clean Tinted Moisturizer as part of \u003cmeta charset=\"utf-8\"\u003e\u003cb data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eAllure Best of Beauty, \u003cmeta charset=\"utf-8\"\u003eCosmopolitan Holy Grail Awards 2021, \u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan class=\"s1\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eWomen’s Health Beauty Awards,\u003c\/b\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"s1\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eNew Beauty Awards, \u003c\/b\u003eand\u003c\/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"s1\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eSELF Healthy Beauty Awards\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003c\/span\u003eCruelty-Free and Formulated without Gluten\u003c\/p\u003e"}
