<div class="product-grid-item js-product-wrapper js-grid-product " data-title="Glowy Super Gel" data-price="28.00" data-variant="32377073238076" data-product-handle="glowy-super-gel-luminizer">

  
  <script type="application/json" class="js-product-data" data-id="4455329759292" data-handle="glowy-super-gel-luminizer">
    {"id":4455329759292,"title":"Glowy Super Gel","handle":"glowy-super-gel-luminizer","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cmeta charset=\"utf-8\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe one and only glow — Saie hello to Glowy Super Gel, a lightweight multipurpose illuminator with a refreshing gel formula that gives an effortless radiance without glitter or strobe. There are no limits with how to use this iconic glow in a bottle: wear it alone, with makeup, mixed into skincare or wherever you want skin that glows from within.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan aria-label=\"\" class=\"c-mrkdwn__br\" data-stringify-type=\"paragraph-break\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePowered by Saie Science, this non-comedogenic gel formula is supercharged with ultra-fine Micropearl, skin-quenching plant-derived Squalane, and moisturizing Glycerin. Glowy Super Gel is now available in three universal shades: Starglow (universal champagne glow), Sunglow (universal bronze gold glow), and NEW! Roseglow (universal rose gold glow).\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan aria-label=\"\" class=\"c-mrkdwn__br\" data-stringify-type=\"paragraph-break\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCruelty-Free, Gluten-Free, Non-Comedogenic and Vegan\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan aria-label=\"\" class=\"c-mrkdwn__br\" data-stringify-type=\"paragraph-break\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eBest of 2022 Beauty - The Quality Edit\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eBest Clean Highlighter - Editorialist’s 2021 Triple Threat Beauty Awards\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","published_at":"2020-02-12T07:03:27-05:00","created_at":"2020-02-07T11:17:19-05:00","vendor":"Saiehello","type":"","tags":["allure-2024","bestseller","bronzing","bronzing drops","dimethicone-free","dry-skin","dullness","essential oil-free","face","formulated-without-gluten","fragrance-free","glamour-2023","hyperpigmentation","multi-use","oily-skin","soy-free","